LaueG exists two versions, a Release version for software users and a Developer version for me, or now possibly you.
The two versions are identical in functionality except the Developer version can build new Release installations.
The Release version also contains the full source code and commented versions of the SCILAB script files.

====== Installing the Developer version of LaueG ======

Install SCILAB version 5.5.2 from www.scilab.org/news/scilab-552-release or ????

Copy the contents of the Develop\ folder of this git to the folder C:\DevApps\LaueG.
If you don't use this folder then you have to edit laueg.sce and change the following link.

Create a link using the Target:
  %SystemDrive%\Program Files\scilab-5.5.2\bin\WScilex.exe -nb -f "C:\DevApps\LaueG\laueg.sce"
and Start in:
  C:\DevApps\LaueG\
You can also change the icon for this link to
  %SystemDrive%\Program Files\scilab-5.5.2\laueg\laueg_icon.ico
